data.name: textBox1.Text
data.value: FinancialPAL is designed to monitor users' financial behaviors and promote positive financial habits. It serves as a personal financial ledger, offering functionalities such as expense and liability tracking to monitor spending against income. Additionally, the application includes features for income and savings management, allowing users to keep tabs on their financial resources. The budgeting feature assists users in creating well-defined budgets within set limits. Should users wish to share feedback or suggestions with administrators, they can utilize the feedback feature provided.
